The quote inspires us to develop the strength and resilience needed to bounce back from disappointments and keep moving forward towards our goals.

Overall, this quote is a testament to Mandela's unwavering spirit and his belief in the power of the human will to triumph over adversity. It continues to motivate and inspire people around the world to face their struggles with courage and determination.
